plyTime":"2018-01-03T02:04:33.000Z","msg":"你就係個仔?😂"},{"pid":"f04e6036a59571fc177b7b62f48ebca5f9081b67","tid":517800,"uid":1667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52be1fa053c3c69d365a57f6d25baac6ce6a7498","tid":517800,"uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"佢個仔接手後已經變左垃圾都有人食😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T02:05:25.000Z","msg":"直情係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b7b4611d8464df6c22c4b3ccb98f06fa463b90","tid":517800,"uid":79410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"560f18f78e72834530076c21acdd1fe091a51215","tid":517800,"uid":36049,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d7950f2baef4d2796d075730945c4635a9d12b2d","tid":517800,"uid":30707,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"喺元朗食親都肚痾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"呢句真<br />\n狗也不食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n199x 年。 我讀元中時就成日去食。真係幾好食。<br />\n之後2000年開始唔得。水準下降。裝修前已經食親都肚屙<br />\n前2年佢裝修完。味道已經唔係一般。係已經難食。一樣食完又屙。仲要細碗咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad535ff06f4b7c44e75b47e593abbd8bed3f934","tid":517800,"uid":38781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"舊時讀中學成日食，見證住佢裝修見證住佢變質。佢老豆既老豆見到真係會想一巴打死呢個仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩裝完修睇佢鋪入面啲介紹，話個仔係外國讀完BBA返來應用返啲理論，用中央工場控制成本，講到話要確保食物質素。現家見佢開完一間又一間已經知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n人地外國唔計歐美，近近地日本台灣諸如泰國既小店都會因為想保留風味一手一腳咁自己落鋪自已捱，香港人一心為錢真係咩都得，欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39021b06763ac4965a839d6598a712910f72f26","tid":517800,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"通常所謂既老字號，一有分店就死得"},{"pid":"212300f3149e05c57b9495a9c40775c98a6c8e63","tid":517800,"ui